{"tid":1777040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（急）周五財委會警甴加薪（無意外就會通過）","createTime":"2019-12-10T02:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T14:47:44.000Z","uid":291354,"like":92,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"6999bcb80142ecb2c6918e4e4b1097a456879279","tid":1777040,"uid":291354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 今個星期五立法會財委會就會繼續審議「公務員加薪」, 入面就包括警甴加薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知大家對警甴既憤怒有幾多, 定純粹過下口癮算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上星期「公務員+警甴加薪」已經傾左兩個鐘, <br />\n今個星期五（13/12）財委會朝早開2個鐘（0845-1045）, 晏晝再開3個鐘（1600-1900）, 基本上如果照常開會討論就可以今個星期成功加薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即使民主派係入面抗爭, 保皇黨主席同埋立法會保安都可以好輕易咁趕哂佢地走, 然後一致舉手通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望大家記得, 我地有幾多手足被呢班警甴虐待同老屈, 甚至因為佢地而可能付出自己既十年歲月; 任由佢地無風無浪下可以如常加薪褒獎佢地, 我自問對唔住之前為呢場運動付出同犠牲既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家回夠氣, 係適當時做適當既事, 謝謝大家🙇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d675e1600f4fdb39fb324f06325e1b76a7010f2c","tid":1777040,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日一致通過啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b893814b3f1a55da8bea03aea2ae88b40edda35c","tid":1777040,"uid":183536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6999bcb80142ecb2c6918e4e4b1097a456879279","tid":1777040,"uid":291354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 今個星期五立法會財委會就會繼續審議「公務員加薪」, 入面就包括警甴加薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知大家對警甴既憤怒有幾多, 定純粹過下口癮算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上星期「公務員+警甴加薪」已